00305 /* watch this, being lazy with memory usage */
00306 #define CLOSURE_IS_BSDF(type) (type <= CLOSURE_BSDF_TRANSPARENT_ID)
00307 #define CLOSURE_IS_BSDF_DIFFUSE(type) (type >= CLOSURE_BSDF_DIFFUSE_ID && type <= CLOSURE_BSDF_OREN_NAYAR_ID)
00308 #define CLOSURE_IS_BSDF_GLOSSY(type) (type >= CLOSURE_BSDF_REFLECTION_ID && type <= CLOSURE_BSDF_WESTIN_SHEEN_ID)
00309 #define CLOSURE_IS_BSDF_TRANSMISSION(type) (type >= CLOSURE_BSDF_TRANSLUCENT_ID && type <= CLOSURE_BSDF_GLASS_ID)
00310 #define CLOSURE_IS_VOLUME(type) (type >= CLOSURE_VOLUME_ID && type <= CLOSURE_VOLUME_ISOTROPIC_ID)
00311 #define CLOSURE_IS_EMISSION(type) (type == CLOSURE_EMISSION_ID)
00312 #define CLOSURE_IS_HOLDOUT(type) (type == CLOSURE_HOLDOUT_ID)
00313 #define CLOSURE_IS_BACKGROUND(type) (type == CLOSURE_BACKGROUND_ID)
